# Copie para profiles.yml (mesma pasta que dbt_project.yml).
#   cp profiles.yml.example profiles.yml
# Credenciais ficam no .env (SPARK_THRIFT_*) — não commite profiles.yml com overrides sensíveis.
#
# Com o pacote plugins/sitecustomize instalado, DBT_PROFILES_DIR e .env costumam ser resolvidos
# automaticamente ao rodar o dbt dentro da árvore do repositório.

lakehouse_tasy:
  target: dev
  outputs:
    dev:
      type: spark
      method: thrift
      auth: LDAP
      schema: raw
      host: "{{ env_var('SPARK_THRIFT_HOST') }}"
      port: "{{ env_var('SPARK_THRIFT_PORT', '10009') | as_number }}"
      user: "{{ env_var('SPARK_THRIFT_USER') }}"
      password: "{{ env_var('SPARK_THRIFT_PASSWORD') }}"
      connect_timeout: 180
      connect_retries: 5
      retry_all: true
      server_side_parameters:
        "kyuubi.engine.share.level.subdomain": "dbt"
        "spark.sql.defaultCatalog": "glue_catalog"
        "spark.sql.catalog.spark_catalog": "org.apache.iceberg.spark.SparkSessionCatalog"
        "spark.sql.catalog.spark_catalog.type": "hive"
        "spark.sql.extensions": "org.apache.iceberg.spark.extensions.IcebergSparkSessionExtensions"
        "spark.network.timeout": "900s"
        "spark.rpc.askTimeout": "900s"
        "spark.rpc.lookupTimeout": "300s"
        "spark.executor.heartbeatInterval": "60s"
        "spark.sql.adaptive.enabled": "true"
        "spark.sql.adaptive.coalescePartitions.enabled": "true"
        # Leitura Avro (raw CDC): SPARK-31404 — sem isto, Spark 3 falha em date/timestamp "antigos".
        # CORRECTED = calendário proléptico; LEGACY se os ficheiros forem de Spark 2 / Hive antigo.
        "spark.sql.avro.datetimeRebaseModeInRead": "CORRECTED"
        "spark.sql.avro.dateRebaseModeInRead": "CORRECTED"
